OL,3,CBoss 'fully accepts' Gloucestershire
OL,4,Cfire service was 'institutionally
OL,5,Cracist'
OL,7,FA chief fire officer has apologised on
OL,8,Fbehalf of the service he runs after a
OL,9,Freview found it had been
OL,10,Finstitutionally racist between 1991
OL,11,Fand 2018.
OL,13,FThe review found black firefighters in
OL,14,FGloucestershire were subjected to
OL,15,Fracial slurs, had swastikas put in
OL,16,Ftheir belongings or glass put in their
OL,17,Fshoes. They were also ostracised and
OL,18,Fignored.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
