OL,3,CBoss 'fully accepts' Gloucestershire
OL,4,Cfire service was 'institutionally
OL,5,Cracist'
OL,7,FA review also revealed unsafe
OL,8,Fpractices including when one
OL,9,Ffirefighter, who later took his own
OL,10,Flife, was sent up a platform ladder
OL,11,Fthat was not properly secured which
OL,12,Fwas then made to "sway and spin".
OL,14,FGloucestershire Fire and Rescue
OL,15,FService (GFRS) was placed in special
OL,16,Fmeasures over its performance in July
OL,17,F2022.
