OL,3,CBoss 'fully accepts' Gloucestershire
OL,4,Cfire service was 'institutionally
OL,5,Cracist'
OL,7,FThe review into bullying and racism at
OL,8,Fthe service was commissioned in 2023
OL,9,Fand carried out by the West Midlands
OL,10,FEmployers. It spoke to 40 current and
OL,11,Fprevious staff members and analysed
OL,12,Fmore than 4,500 documents.
OL,14,FIt concluded the service was
OL,15,Finstitutionally racist but is not
OL,16,Finstitutionally racist today. However,
OL,17,Fit did find there is still work to be
OL,18,Fdone within the service.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
