OL,3,CBoss 'fully accepts' Gloucestershire
OL,4,Cfire service was 'institutionally
OL,5,Cracist'
OL,7,FChief fire officer Mark Preece, who
OL,8,Fcommissioned the report in 2023, said
OL,9,Fhe "fully accepts" the findings that
OL,10,Fthe force was institutionally racist.
OL,12,F"I want to apologise to our
OL,13,Ffirefighters and staff past and
OL,14,Fpresent that have been subjected to
OL,15,Fthe horrendous acts of discrimination,
OL,16,For witnessed, whistle-blown and tried
OL,17,Fto support victims as best they could
OL,18,Fwith little or no support.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
