OL,4,Cfire service was 'institutionally
OL,5,Cracist'
OL,7,F"I fully accept the finding that the
OL,8,Fservice was institutionally racist
OL,9,Fbetween 1991 to 2018, and that coupled
OL,10,Fwith a lack of action from those
OL,11,Fleading GFRS during this time made
OL,12,Flife unbearable for our Black and
OL,13,Fethnic minority firefighters.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
