OL,5,Cracist'
OL,7,FThe report says Avanos was "subjected
OL,8,Fto racial slurs and derogatory
OL,9,Fcomments" and found the n word written
OL,10,Fon his T-shirt after a volleyball game.
OL,12,F"Avanos experienced being ignored by
OL,13,Fcolleagues, subjected to intimidating
OL,14,Fstares, and found glass in his shoes.
OL,15,FHis food was tampered with, and
OL,16,Fitching powder was placed in his kit
OL,17,Fand bed," the report says.
OL,19,FSwastikas were also placed in his
OL,20,Fbelongings.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
