OL,7,FMr Biney took his own life in 2017.
OL,8,FHis family say he was a "generous,
OL,9,Ffunny and selfless" man with a "strong
OL,10,Fsense of mischief and humour".
OL,12,FMr James died of a brain tumour in
OL,13,F2019. His family believe was brought
OL,14,Fon by the stress and a hostile working
OL,15,Fenvironment contributed to his
OL,16,Fdeclining health.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
