OL,7,FThe report says Mr James was
OL,8,F"experienced social ostracism and was
OL,9,Fexcluded by his colleagues", saying he
OL,10,Fwas ignored during meals and social
OL,11,Finteractions and management
OL,12,F"manipulated" situations to make him
OL,13,Fappear "unprofessional".
OL,15,FChief fire officer Mr Preece said he
OL,16,Fwants to "work with" the families of
OL,17,Fboth Mr James and Mr Biney.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
