OL,7,F"I want to make it clear that they
OL,8,Fwere not troublemakers, they were
OL,9,Ftrail blazers," he said. "The bravery
OL,10,Fof these individuals and family
OL,11,Fmembers that have spoken up in the
OL,12,Fpast and again now are breaking down
OL,13,Fbarriers as well as challenging
OL,14,Fignorant, long held views and
OL,15,Fstereotypes.
