OL,7,F"Their dedication to making a change
OL,8,Ffor good must be recognised and the
OL,9,Flegacy of everyone reliving the trauma
OL,10,Fmust be lasting and meaningful. We
OL,11,Fwill set the record straight and
OL,12,Fcelebrate their lives and
OL,13,Fcontributions."
OL,15,FMr James' family told ITV News they
OL,16,Fwelcome the report but nothing will
