OL,7,FThey say he suffered "terrible racism"
OL,8,Fwhile working for the fire service,
OL,9,Fsaying staff members would ignore him,
OL,10,Fwould not sit with him at lunch, and
OL,11,Fthat he was ostracised during his time.
OL,13,FIn 2014, Mr James was successful in a
OL,14,Ftribunal against the service over
OL,15,Faccusations he was victimised at work.
OL,16,FHowever a separate claim of racism was
OL,17,Fdismissed.
