OL,7,FHis widow Sarah James said: "I am glad
OL,8,Fthat an independent review has found
OL,9,FGloucestershire Fire and Rescue
OL,10,FService to have been institutionally
OL,11,Fracist during the time that John
OL,12,Fworked there.
OL,14,F"He suffered terribly because of the
OL,15,Fcolour of his skin. But even with all
OL,16,Fthe apologies I still feel bitter. It
OL,17,Fwon't bring him back."
